## 3. Core Features

### Feature 1 — Virtual Watch Box Display

The centerpiece of the product. A high-fidelity, grid-style visual layout that replicates the look and feel of a real watch box. This is the first thing users see and the primary interaction surface.

**User Stories**
- As a collector, I want to see my watches arranged in a realistic box so that I feel like I'm interacting with my physical collection.
- As a user, I want to customize the number of slots, box material, and color so the box reflects my personal aesthetic.
- As a user, I want to drag and drop watches between slots so I can experiment with different arrangements.

**Functional Requirements**
- Grid layout with configurable slot count (1, 2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12 watches)
- Each slot displays an accurate, high-resolution watch dial visualization (dial, case, strap visible)
- Box customization: material (wood, leather, carbon fiber, velvet), color, padding style
- Drag-and-drop slot reordering
- Empty slot placeholder with an "Add Watch" CTA on hover
- **Hover interaction:** floating watch card appears above slot (see Section 2 — Core Interaction Pattern)
- **Click interaction:** right-hand sidebar slides open with full watch detail (see Section 2)
- Active slot is highlighted with a gold border accent while sidebar is open
- Responsive layout: adapts from widescreen to mobile

**MVP Scope**
- Dark luxury aesthetic with 6 default slots in a 3×2 grid
- Hover card with brand, name, reference, size, and estimated value
- Click-to-sidebar with full spec sheet and quick action buttons (Find For Sale, Sell, Swap Strap)
- SVG dial visualization per watch
- Empty slot with `+` Add Watch state
- Box color selector (4–6 presets)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| Box Grid Display | 3×2 dark luxury grid with dial visualizations | P0 – Must Have |
| Hover Card | Floating mini-card on slot hover with key specs | P0 – Must Have |
| Click Sidebar | Slide-out right panel with full detail and actions | P0 – Must Have |
| Slot Customization | Slot count, material, and color options | P0 – Must Have |
| Empty Slot State | `+` Add Watch CTA on hover for empty slots | P0 – Must Have |
| Drag & Drop | Reorder watches between slots | P1 – High |
| Responsive Layout | Adapts to mobile and tablet | P1 – High |

