### Feature 4 — Playground Mode & Saved Views

A dedicated experimentation zone where users build "dream boxes" — fantasy collections unconstrained by what they own. Uses the same hover card + click-to-sidebar interaction as My Collection (Section 2), with sidebar content adapted for the Playground context.

**User Stories**
- As a watch enthusiast, I want to build a dream box of watches I aspire to own so I can share it with friends and the community.
- As a user, I want to save multiple box configurations (e.g., "All Chronographs", "If I Win the Lottery") and switch between them easily.
- As a user, I want to share my box publicly with a link so others can browse my taste.

**Functional Requirements**
- Separate "Playground" tab/mode distinct from "My Collection"
- Access to the full watch database (not just owned watches)
- **Hover card** shows the same mini-card as My Collection (brand, name, ref, size, market value)
- **Click sidebar** in Playground context shows: full specs, current market price range, "Add to My Collection" and "Find For Sale ↗" CTAs — ownership fields (purchase date, price paid) are hidden since the watch is not owned
- Create, name, and save unlimited box configurations
- Tags and themes for saved boxes (e.g., "Dive Watches", "Under $5K", "Dress Watches")
- Public shareable link for each saved box
- Option to copy another user's shared box to your own Playground
- Side-by-side spec comparison for watches in the same box

**MVP Scope**
- Single playground box with full database access
- Hover card + sidebar using Playground-specific sidebar content
- Save up to 3 named views
- Share via link (view-only)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| Playground Tab | Separate mode for building dream/fantasy boxes | P0 – Must Have |
| Hover Card | Same mini-card as My Collection | P0 – Must Have |
| Playground Sidebar | Spec + market price + Find For Sale / Add to Collection CTAs | P0 – Must Have |
| Save Named Views | Save and label multiple box configurations | P0 – Must Have |
| Public Share Link | Shareable URL for any saved box | P1 – High |
