**User Stories**
- As a user with a collection of dive watches, I want the platform to suggest similar or complementary watches I might love.
- As a user browsing Royal Oak references, I want to see strap suggestions that match the bracelet aesthetic.

**Functional Requirements**
- Recommendation panel: "You May Also Like" — shown below or beside the main box
- Signals used: watches in My Collection, Playground saves, search queries, affiliate clicks, brands followed
- Watch suggestions with affiliate deep-links to Chrono24, WatchBox, eBay
- Strap suggestions paired to specific watches
- Watch box suggestions (physical boxes) based on slot count and aesthetic
- Optional: demographic / onboarding quiz to cold-start recommendations

**MVP Scope**
- Rule-based suggestions (same brand, similar complication, similar price range)
- "More from this brand" and "Collectors also love" panels
- Affiliate links on all suggestions

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---|---|---|
| Rule-Based Suggestions | Same brand/complication/price recommendations | P0 – Must Have |
