## 6. Success Metrics

### 6.1 Engagement
- Time spent per session — target: >5 minutes
- Watches added per user — target: >4 in first session
- Box saves per user — target: >2 within first week
- Return visit rate — target: >40% within 7 days

### 6.2 Revenue
- Affiliate click-through rate — target: >8% of product impressions
- Affiliate conversion rate — target: 1–3% (platform-dependent)
- Revenue per user per month — target: $0.50–$2.00 at scale
- Sponsored content fill rate — target: >70% of available slots

### 6.3 Growth
- Email list size at launch — target: 1,000+
- Monthly active users at Month 3 — target: 2,500
- Monthly active users at Month 12 — target: 25,000
- Organic search traffic from watch-related queries

